(NULL, 'Do you offer "Cash on Delivery" option?', 1, '{"charges":"25"}', 'cod', 1, 90, 1, 1, 3,'The Cash on Delivery (COD) feature allows the customer to pay for the goods at the time of delivery at their footstep. You can charge extra amount in COD, if needed. If you do not wish to charge extra to your customers for COD facility write ‘0’ (zero) in the popup.', tblprfx_),
